      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LINCOLN LOVER NZ (7) has the hoof on the till after placing in both outings off a spell. Raced parked when beaten 3m into second at this circuit and distance when resuming before coming from the back line for a 1.8m third at Pinjarra on Monday. Tactics will be crucial from this draw but he should be close to his peak now. MAJOR MOVES NZ (3) put the writing on the wall when second two starts ago then registered an easy win last start, scoring by 8.8 metres at Bunbury. Likely to get the favours from this nice draw so another win is not out of the question. MY MACHANE (5) is on the radar off a win from a similar barrier to this two back at Bunbury. STRONG THE STRIKER (2) is worth some thought from a good draw.",
